-- Carbon Permit, Energy Options Broker Genus Leaves OTC Europe
-- B y   A l e s s a n d r o   V i t e l l i
-- 2013-04-08T14:57:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-08/carbon-permit-energy-options-broker-genus-leaves-otc-europe.html
Brett Genus, an energy options
broker at OTC  Europe  LLP in London, left the company on March
28, he said today by telephone.  Genus joined the company in November 2010, handling carbon
emissions and crude oil options. Before that he spent two years
at Evolution Markets LLC in London broking carbon emissions
futures and options. OTC Europe confirmed the departure in an e-
mail.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alessandro Vitelli in London at 
 avitelli1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
